{
  "stem": "2533.5",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And then he wasn't well, and I didn't have warm clothes, because we were-- we were told we are going to a tropical-- semi-tropical or tropical country, and all our luggage was not together with us.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "But I had a American woolen sleeping bag, and that maybe saved his life, because it was so cold on the train.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "August, when we arrived to [INAUDIBLE], it was snow almost to the place where we were going to-- to live.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And the mountain, the Blue Mountain [INAUDIBLE] you know, you could walk out to the mountains.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And he was taken straight away to hospital.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "I went to-- to report that he's not well.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And the doctor came.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "He looked him over.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And he said, there's no time for ambulance.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "He took him with me in the car to the hospital.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And he had measles, pneumonia, and gastroenteritis.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And then they didn't find out that he was allergic to penicillin.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "After a few injections, he got all rash in his mouth.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "He couldn't eat.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "He couldn't drink.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "They kept him there for 6 weeks.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "I stayed there the whole time in--",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "He was 2 and 1/2.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But my husband-- they were all on contracts, so the government had taken them away for work.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He went to Richmond to work for the Air Force as manual labor.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I stayed in [INAUDIBLE] 'til Andrew will get better.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And then when he got better, he couldn't even speak.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "He couldn't even walk.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But somehow, you know, he recovered pretty well.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And it was-- I went to a camp place, Greta near Maitland.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "There were two camps.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "One was called the Silver City and one was called the Chocolate City.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I was in the Silver City.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
